    public class BusImpl
extends ExtensionElementImpl
implements Bus
    An implementation of the model object 'Bus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Base Voltage
    • Sub Area Flag
    • Sec No
    • Parent
    • Network
    • To Branch List
    • From Branch List
    • Bus Sec List
